Berlusconi Flies to Summer Residence in Sardinia, Ansa Says

-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 
2011-08-06T15:18:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-06/berlusconi-flies-to-summer-residence-in-sardinia-ansa-says.html
Italian Prime Minister  Silvio Berlusconi  arrived in Sardinia this afternoon to spend at least
a weekend at his summer residence on the island, news agency
Ansa reported.  Berlusconi said the government was working “without
interruption” and that he would return to the capital on Aug. 9
at the latest, according to Ansa.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Armorel Kenna in Milan at 
 akenna@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net  